						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/Ten-year-probe-reveals-oceans-in-peril" title="Ten-year probe reveals oceans in peril" alt="link">Ten-year probe reveals oceans in peril</a></h2>

	
					<p>Scientists from 82 countries work to complete the decade-long global research effort called the Census of Marine Life. The census will eventually produce global maps of species richness. The ultimate legacy of the census is that it has shifted the attention and imaginations of many to the all-important oceans, which are still less well-known than the surface of the moon (Source: Stephen Leahy, IPS, 11 November 2008). </p>
							<p><span class="date">1/12/2008</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/Dossiers/Commodities/Fisheries/Related-developments/Ten-year-probe-reveals-oceans-in-peril">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
